joined reports creates multiple report blocks providing different views of data
report folders can be shared to users , roles and groups
dashboard viewer setting enables user to see data based on his access levels.
cross filters are used to include/exclude records on related objects and sub filters can be added to further refine the results.
dashboard components:
metric component - display one key value
guauge compenent-single value within a range of values
lightning table-200 records and 10 columns in tabular format from any field in source eport type

